{"tid":1297791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國破家亡 年輕唔可以再係藉口","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T00:45:48.000Z","uid":45206,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c66c04114dbd80b9f4dae2d2c31279490c935d39","tid":1297791,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"今日有好多人真心膠出咗嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登好多人得十幾歲 但年紀細唔可以再係藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國破家亡 就算你喺青少年 而家都要成為一個男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好問點解唔公平 唔好問點解冇童年<br />\n<br />\n因為我都好想睇下詩詞歌賦 唔撚係日日喺度睇共產黨新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係戰時就係咁 成個東亞過去一百年都係咁！呢個直頭係東亞人嘅共同命運！！！<br />\n<br />\n希望cd-rom 同真心膠 唔好因為咁而唔再出嚟 因為最重要都係香港 大家都係為件事好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24adf2ae02e9f89d40d57725f2702d01a4906cd3","tid":1297791,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9172d84fc55c2ecedb20f2658670633dc2ac04b8","tid":1297791,"uid":149575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:48:47.000Z","msg":"UP乜9<br />\n成個運動根本係後生仔企出黎多<br />\n你唔問下D 30~50 中年去左邊?"},{"pid":"9f835f2202366bd9e0cd4c1d5a959302e7a863bd","tid":1297791,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9172d84fc55c2ecedb20f2658670633dc2ac04b8","tid":1297791,"uid":149575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:48:47.000Z","msg":"UP乜9<br />\n成個運動根本係後生仔企出黎多<br />\n你唔問下D 30~50 中年去左邊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:01:03.000Z","msg":"我同意前線係後生仔多<br />\n但其實後面都有好多打工仔 7.7勁多中年人你有無見到<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個唔係重點 重點係無人可以幼稚落去 因爲個cost係香港玩完"},{"pid":"a7f3b4ea1e6331d65bce8a3a82a3f7e095f47146","tid":1297791,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:31:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9df4c4ae6de3f21c02b9ee0b05860e3ee4d8d5e9","tid":1297791,"uid":64159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9172d84fc55c2ecedb20f2658670633dc2ac04b8","tid":1297791,"uid":149575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:48:47.000Z","msg":"UP乜9<br />\n成個運動根本係後生仔企出黎多<br />\n你唔問下D 30~50 中年去左邊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:45:48.000Z","msg":"唔係話啲後生唔出嚟，<br />\n係話緊尋晚啲人以為自己撚緊狗但係呃咗班有心人出去呢樣野on9 同無聊"}]}